      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WIRRULLA HARRY (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.85) in a Grade 6 at Gawler. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Should be very hard to beat this time. ANTECEDENT (5) was drawn the middle last start but pinged the lids and recorded an all-the-way win (20.25) at this track in a Other over 342m. Capable of going well again. BONNIE DIVA (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (20.52) last time in a Other at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Worth following up. LOCKABA NITRO (4) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
